gobblin.util.request_allocation

Interface PushDownRequestor<T extends Request>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<T>, Requestor<T>

    public interface PushDownRequestor<T extends Request>
extends Requestor<T>
    A Requestor that can provide an Iterator of Requests already sorted by the input prioritizer. Allows push down of certain prioritizers to more efficient layers.
